-- Perfect World joins consortium offering to buy out Shanda Games 
-- By Sruthi Ramakrishnan in Bangalore
-- Mon Apr 21, 2014 06:55AM EDT
-- None



April 21 (Reuters) - China's online game developer Perfect World Co Ltd <PWRD.O> said it joined the consortium offering to buy rival Shanda Games Ltd <GAME.O>.

Perfect World said it would buy 30.3 million class A Shanda Games shares for $100 million from Shanda Interactive Entertainment Ltd, a shareholder in Shanda Games. [ID:nPn6RmNpB]